test Package¶

TestClafers Module¶

Created on Sep 15, 2013

@author: ezulkosk

test.TestClafers.getTestSet()¶
test.TestClafers.print_separate(x)¶
test.TestClafers.run()¶

Runs the Z3-translator on each pair (file, numInstances) in tests, and ensures that the number of generated models equals numInstances.

test.TestClafers.runForOne()¶

Runs the Z3-translator on each pair file in tests, and outputs one model for each, if satisfiable.
